description: Returns the results of a completed email archive search job.

parameters.name: SearchId
parameters.description: The identifier of the completed search job.

nested_items.name: Rows
nested_items.description: The list of email result objects matching the search criteria.

nested_items.name: ArchivedMessageId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the archived message.

nested_items.name: Cc
nested_items.description: The email addresses in the CC header.

nested_items.name: Date
nested_items.description: The date the email was sent.

nested_items.name: From
nested_items.description: The RCPT FROM given by the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: Helo
nested_items.description: The HELO used by the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: To
nested_items.description: All SMTP TO entries given by the host from which the email was received.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: From
nested_items.description: The email address of the sender.

nested_items.name: HasAttachments
nested_items.description: A flag indicating if the email has attachments.

nested_items.name: InReplyTo
nested_items.description: The email message ID this is a reply to.

nested_items.name: IngressPointId
nested_items.description: The ID of the ingress endpoint through which the email was received.

nested_items.name: MessageId
nested_items.description: The unique message ID of the email.

nested_items.name: ReceivedHeaders
nested_items.description: The received headers from the email delivery path.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: ReceivedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the email was received.

nested_items.name: SenderHostname
nested_items.description: The name of the host from which the email was received.

nested_items.name: SenderIpAddress
nested_items.description: Mail archived with Mail Manager: The IP address of the client that connects to the ingress endpoint.
Mail archived with Mail Manager: The IP address of the client that connects to the ingress endpoint.
Mail sent through a configuration set with the archiving option enabled: The IP address of the client that makes the SendEmail API call.

nested_items.name: SourceArn
nested_items.description: Specifies the archived email source, identified by either a Rule Set's ARN with an Archive action, or a Configuration Set's Archive ARN.

nested_items.name: Subject
nested_items.description: The subject header value of the email.

nested_items.name: To
nested_items.description: The email addresses in the To header.

nested_items.name: XMailer
nested_items.description: The user agent that sent the email.

nested_items.name: XOriginalMailer
nested_items.description: The original user agent that sent the email.

nested_items.name: XPriority
nested_items.description: The priority level of the email.
